title: the ten year icon
body: I was wondering if the party poro icons were still being given out as some friends on League have gotten tem but me and another player I know still do not?

replies.body: They gifts are still being given out, rest easy!  There are a lot of accounts to gift so it will need to take some time, but you can stay updated through our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Patience!
thank you, just wondering. and thn for rito kayle.
